CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780081925
OL,3,CHealth professionals challenge safety
OL,4,Cclaims by UK Sunbed Association
OL,6,FThey say: "Whether it is a new or
OL,7,Fchanging mole, a sore that doesn't
OL,8,Fheal, or an area of skin that is
OL,9,Funusual for you, it's important to get
OL,10,Fit checked out.
OL,12,F"It probably won't be cancer, but if
OL,13,Fit is, spotting it at an early stage
OL,14,Fcan make all the difference."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
